    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this absolute stunner. It's in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
