    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 996.2 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of analog precision. This specimen features the 3.6L flat-six powerplant, fully addressed with an LN Engineering IMS retrofit and a new Rear Main Seal (RMS) to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, tactile throws, channeling power through an all-wheel-drive system that maintains perfect torque distribution. The chassis remains factory-spec with M030 sport suspension, providing exceptional lateral stability and minimal body roll. Unsprung weight is optimized via authentic Turbo-look hollow-spoke wheels wrapped in N-rated Michelin Pilot Sport rubber. The exterior retains its original factory luster with consistent paint-meter readings across all panels, while the interior shows no bolster wear or UV degradation on the dash. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle with a comprehensive service history and zero deferred maintenance.",
